txt.en: 'Are you ready to proceed? Finishing this quest will award completion of Volume III Book 12 of the Epic quest.'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book 12 of the Epic quest series of Volume III.

'Are you ready to complete Volume III, Book 12? You will bypass a journey through West Rohan.'\n\n'It is your decision. If you would like to skip Volume III Book 12 of the Epic quest, speak to me once more. Meow!'
